<plot>Jonathon, Art, and Crispin are profiled as killers with disparate passions in this short film. As the killers bury their victims and the secrets the heinous crime conceals, their dispositions are showcased in the process. This is the story not of what is being buried beneath the ground but what can be found buried deep within oneself after the crime has been committed.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087001</url></doc>
